{"tid":2022641,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】板野友美IG罕有曬性感相　小蠻腰先係網友重點","createTime":"2020-05-18T12:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T16:32:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4df8aa03ab70bfbff744ad3b7d938ba688a227a","tid":2022641,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"知名女子偶像團體《AKB48》前成員板野友美，是《AKB48》初始成員之一，不過她在2013年宣布畢業，期後以歌影視為目標發展。<br />\n<br />\n板野友美今天（18日）IG發布一張照片，表示非常期待夏天的來臨，因為現時日本天氣約18度至20度。而網友的重點便是她穿着的衣服，板野友美穿着一件印有士多啤利的白色吊帶背心，這次是她罕有地展示「事業線」之外，她的小蠻腰更為吸睛，不禁讓網友覺得平常在IG較為密實的板野友美原來身材這麼好。"},{"pid":"4d038d65d85c3066b09b08ad3dd900531e761849","tid":2022641,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4510781/org/520df062decbbc0131f3d696cb4ec372.jpg/vaxWgTb-KLk01K2p_oe5MRXys1IAqZCd5GXpvORl6bw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4510781%2Forg%2F520df062decbbc0131f3d696cb4ec372.jpg%2FvaxWgTb-KLk01K2p_oe5MRXys1IAqZCd5GXpvORl6bw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=9c138044&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cbee96045d39e44d522f7f1fddd6a8150ae3b64","tid":2022641,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4510782/org/65d9b3a3fa998c7470b94c5957aa06ec.jpg/wMIVmB08JIsIwBKl6DXM6lLrTG2YujVInIGlVJyBpVQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4510782%2Forg%2F65d9b3a3fa998c7470b94c5957aa06ec.jpg%2FwMIVmB08JIsIwBKl6DXM6lLrTG2YujVInIGlVJyBpVQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9d7d8500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4510825/org/2259579f407a26c2cceaea9615757ce9.jpg/NXd7n6uiKshyVCqjnTHCcBvaxBYksOHo15fryNeX68g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4510825%2Forg%2F2259579f407a2